file.name: nested-array-example.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.0.0
  title: Nested array mock test
paths:
  /:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserArray'

components:
  schemas:
    UserArray:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/User"
      example:
      - id: 1
        name: Arthur Dent
      - id: 2
        name: Ford Prefect
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          example: 0
        name:
          type: string
          example: Marvin
